title: AMERICAN HORROR STORIES Episode 6 Breakdown, Easter Eggs & Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment:
I think there is one more episode of American Horror Stories before DOUBLE FEATURE! What did you guys think of FERAL?

Check out my AH Stories Playlist:
I wish they explained why the missing son become the leader of the cannibals, like wtf was that all about lmao…
You missed the end where he licked the blood off of his finger. His mom told him not to lick his fingers at the beginning of the episode.

When the creatures broke into the house I was like "oh okay they look creepy, finally we're getting somewhere" then I realize there was only 6 minutes left in the show and I knew the ending was going to be bad
The episode had so many potential! They could've used Cody more. The story was too short to be concluded.
description:
FX and Hulu's AHS spinoff series AMERICAN HORROR STORIES has just released episode 6 FERAL. In this video I break it all down including easter eggs from past seasons and the AHS universe.
